The following components are based on or inspired by vmalert:

  - Alert state machine (Inactive -> Pending -> Firing) and evaluation
    loop design (rule/ package)
  - Rule configuration YAML format and validation logic (config/ package)
  - Rule identity hashing scheme: FNV-64a of expression + name + labels
  - Alertmanager v2 notification payload format (notifier/ package)
  - Conformance tests ported from vmalert's TestAlertingRule_Exec
    (rule/conformance_test.go)

